{"tid":2444661,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【娛樂人物】電影業俠女 開高先戲院 播《理大圍城》 曾麗芬勇字當頭：人棄我取","createTime":"2021-03-13T03:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T07:10:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2450c24de4a99016822dea846f1d3d126113717a","tid":2444661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T03:56:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210313/II7EHV4XOBEABNXICA5ICIY47E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210313%2FII7EHV4XOBEABNXICA5ICIY47E%2F&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=b7f65cb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210313%2FII7EHV4XOBEABNXICA5ICIY47E%2F&h=e9d1b692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210313/II7EHV4XOBEABNXICA5ICIY47E/</a><br />\n<br />\n【娛樂人物】電影業俠女 開高先戲院 播《理大圍城》 曾麗芬勇字當頭：人棄我取<br />\n<br />\n在香港立足36年的UA戲院隕落，令香港戲迷欷歔不已，不過座落於堅尼地城的高先電影院卻令電影界重拾曙光，董事總經理曾麗芬（Winnie Tsang）出錢出力撐本土電影，在風雨飄搖環境下開戲院，更首度將抗爭紀錄片《理大圍城》搬上商營戲院播放，被黃修平稱為電影業俠女的Winnie，勇字當頭，行事作風「人棄我取」，多年來排除萬難實現電影夢，箇中有血有淚。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【叫好叫座】由發行變投資本土製作<br />\n撰文：何永寧<br />\n<br />\n攝影：仇志德<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：《理大圍城》戲飛十分鐘售罄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xwJDwBj5zf3rjPYZirIxKT3jx-U=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MXBGSDYTFZHM7GNPCDQ5EVQEDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxwJDwBj5zf3rjPYZirIxKT3jx-U%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMXBGSDYTFZHM7GNPCDQ5EVQEDM.jpg&h=91749ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一直專注電影發行及支持本土電影製作的曾麗芬，早前於堅尼地城開辦高先電影院，繼續尋電影夢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D8NgZ_ZS6ftGKbL2NzlfEs0uZO4=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EX3CXXPQYBGNPLW6M5HU4EXX7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD8NgZ_ZS6ftGKbL2NzlfEs0uZO4%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEX3CXXPQYBGNPLW6M5HU4EXX7Q.jpg&h=00dd2b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曾麗芬最初入職嘉禾時是當秘書，當幾任主管離職後她才慢慢學會買片及宣傳工作。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q4XLFRkr_koaKDuVqkwh40xu6KM=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QT2YWHWYF5C7FFKGZNUKV4VPZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq4XLFRkr_koaKDuVqkwh40xu6KM%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQT2YWHWYF5C7FFKGZNUKV4VPZI.jpg&h=38a9eb2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曾麗芬（右二）打滾影圈多年，認識包括陳慧琳經理人鍾珍（左二）及製片廖鳳平（右一）等眾多電影人。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n武肺疫情重創電影業，當UA戲院因蝕錢抽身全退，曾麗芬卻眾人皆醒我獨醉，在堅尼地城開戲院，逆巿下投資拍本土電影。高先曾投資的有陳果導演的《那夜凌晨，我坐上了旺角開往大埔的紅VAN》及黃修平導演的《狂舞派》等，行內人講笑話Winnie近年講得最多一句是「我搞掂」，不少新晉導演會找她幫手籌集資金，Winnie笑笑口反問︰「邊個講㗎？係咪黃修平呀。」她因為欣賞黃修平對電影的熱誠，最後投資拍《狂舞派》，大收1,316萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n排片更自由 可播心愛電影<br />\n<br />\nWinnie說拍片及揀片喜歡「人棄我取」，所以新導演都愛找她合作，遭黃修平於訪問中形容她為現代俠女︰「。。。。。。。。。。。」而俠女精神亦體現在她夠膽於旗下戲院上映抗爭紀綠片《理大圍城》，並為電影發聲平反，肯定它的價值。<br />\n<br />\n高先電影成立初期以發行為主，Winnie自滿打得最漂亮一仗，是90年代在嘉禾時引入。。。。。。。。。。。︰「要講番嗰時《十年》香港唔係我哋發行，因為冇戲院同佢做。開頭係一間戲院做，後期做到好多院線加入，突然就冇咗戲院，佢哋嚟搵我哋，仲有邊啲可以做，高先就同佢哋做iTunes、Google Play，我哋係負責海外發行，本地發行喺佢哋自己搵院。」<br />\n<br />\n搞戲院一直是Winnie的。。。。。。。。。。︰「有冇諗退休？起碼要做十年，因為呢間戲院至少十年。跟住姨甥Felix接手，佢比我更愛香港電影，係我接班人。」戲院上月已開幕，她表示第二間陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-rWV4k4ZWM2ydfIhHo5dmLwWzig=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FYIBR4ZP5ZEXTDSKHM4FOVOEIQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-rWV4k4ZWM2ydfIhHo5dmLwWzig%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFYIBR4ZP5ZEXTDSKHM4FOVOEIQ.jpg&h=ba2f39e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曾麗芬的辦公室枱頭放了當年跟里安納度狄卡比奧的合照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QV3CGE7phNIbHY9br6A4XfOB0wU=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z32DE7CJNBFZBESKPRQTECHWNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQV3CGE7phNIbHY9br6A4XfOB0wU%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ32DE7CJNBFZBESKPRQTECHWNI.jpg&h=505452a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■高先電影投資的電影奪過不少獎項，曾麗芬視比她更愛香港電影的姨甥Felix（小圖）為接班人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獲李嘉誠聘用 寧揀入嘉禾<br />\n<br />\nWinnie當年自商學院修畢秘書課程就入嘉禾︰「嗰時聖心讀秘書科，校長介紹我入嘉禾，呢份係第一份亦係唯一一份工，爸爸又介紹我入長江（實業）做秘書，當時長江請咗我，但我唔想囉。面試見我嘅係李嘉誠同洪小蓮，入到去爸爸同李生講『我個女，啱啱畢業』，李生話『好吖......』，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nWinnie記得在嘉禾年代，。。。。。。。。。反而成龍較少請食飯︰「大哥鍾意同我哋傾偈，以前公司較細，人少好好玩，許冠傑試過聖誕節坐喺reception彈結他唱歌。」。。。。。。。，Golden Scene才正式成立。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/of8Eej0x1wAtnMy4GncyGLKrj-c=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3GRDPP6REBC6ZGEPYBEJXDB3II.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fof8Eej0x1wAtnMy4GncyGLKrj-c%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3GRDPP6REBC6ZGEPYBEJXDB3II.jpg&h=749db6f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李嘉誠"},{"pid":"c5acb4aa1d2f17bd84c425b2d577e779f5cb7cb6","tid":2444661,"uid":9,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"winnie 好有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c234f7d9170b75fd1aaf49cb1c5dccc814b6cd","tid":2444661,"uid":1646,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"個幾月前仲要比蘋果屈左撐安心出行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad772de055b56fa928fce91dda38edfac8764e1","tid":2444661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"堅尼地城 高先電影院(Golden Scene) 位置<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gGbisS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gGbisS</a>"},{"pid":"fd6dace2ad0b5caa72fcdf69f967729b2112b962","tid":2444661,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:32:30.000Z","msg":"撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5bababb9d16546935ecaf9fcc968f3aed4d6b3","tid":2444661,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f79374cd1190e352aa930a8af589f158b89609c","tid":2444661,"uid":8075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:39:37.000Z","msg":"撐高先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ab72bbe4158db57e6b526b4b8ca653a22031d7","tid":2444661,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a1f1d3df628873e5fcd6cc7e58c84033cf7226","tid":2444661,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af17a095d15a589e15cac38caaf7fad55af496b","tid":2444661,"uid":74163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"李生話『好吖......』，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n佢阿爸都幾有頭有臉"},{"pid":"526315e7dc6c50b2a61807a849a8a95c3484c41d","tid":2444661,"uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49c234f7d9170b75fd1aaf49cb1c5dccc814b6cd","tid":2444661,"uid":1646,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"個幾月前仲要比蘋果屈左撐安心出行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:51:35.000Z","msg":"蘋果有咩做唔出呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698b9fc3638795bbc4a71f0be51fdd620b46e014","tid":2444661,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:36:47.000Z","msg":"後生幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24345f80b9170c4582cd67e75629d6e85a9ac0fa","tid":2444661,"uid":271397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:41:07.000Z","msg":"由秘書做到開戲院, 好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f732b76745ee3e78893f7964ab733457d9bc8b59","tid":2444661,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"Felix Tsang Letterboxd, 真係睇唔少戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://boxd.it/tjcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fboxd.it%2Ftjcf&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=e231a752\" target=\"_blank\">https://boxd.it/tjcf</a>"},{"pid":"dc164fec91b0ee3072149d